# =============================================================================
# PROTECTED — DO NOT CHANGE THESE IN PRODUCTION WITHOUT GUARDIAN APPROVAL
# =============================================================================
# These are the canonical PUBLIC base URLs advertised to every developer,
# integrator, bank, and SDK that consumes the Kang Open Banking API.
# Changing them is a BREAKING CHANGE for every integrator on the platform.
#
# This file is documentation-only. It exists to record the agreed values
# and to give future contributors a single source of truth.
#
# Real runtime values live in the auto-managed .env file (which must not be
# edited by hand) and in Cloudflare Worker environment variables.
#
# If you think you need to change one of these URLs, open a GitHub issue
# tagged [api-change] FIRST and follow the process in API_DOC_LOCK.md.
# =============================================================================

# Public production API hostname — advertised in OpenAPI, SDKs, docs.
KOB_PUBLIC_API_BASE_URL=https://api.kangopenbanking.com/v1

# Public sandbox API hostname — advertised in OpenAPI, SDKs, docs.
KOB_PUBLIC_SANDBOX_BASE_URL=https://sandbox-api.kangopenbanking.com/v1

# Public OpenAPI spec locations.
KOB_PUBLIC_OPENAPI_JSON_URL=https://kangopenbanking.com/openapi.json
KOB_PUBLIC_OPENAPI_YAML_URL=https://kangopenbanking.com/openapi.yaml

# =============================================================================
# NEVER expose internal infrastructure URLs in developer-facing content.
# =============================================================================
# The Supabase project hostname (*.supabase.co) is a backend implementation
# detail. It MUST NEVER appear in:
#   - any page under /developer/*
#   - any rendered code example, screenshot, or diagram
#   - the OpenAPI spec
#   - the Postman collection
#   - the prerendered HTML produced by vite-plugin-prerender-docs.ts
#
# The Cloudflare Worker is responsible for terminating public traffic on
# api.kangopenbanking.com and sandbox-api.kangopenbanking.com and for
# proxying it to the underlying Supabase Edge Functions. Code and docs
# always speak to the public hostnames.
# =============================================================================
